data.description: Charming four-bedroom home in desirable Romeoville.  Boasting a classic design and spacious layout. This residence offers a perfect blend of comfort. style and convenience. Large bay window in the living room,   laminate hardwood floors in living room, kitchen has SS appliances, newer washer and dryer. Kitchen has ample counter space, large windows, and plenty of storage. Four large bedrooms and a large backyard with a treehouse and shed. The backyard is a private oasis perfect for outdoor activities, gardening or unwinding after long day. Home is located in Romeoville community providing easy access to a range of amenities including shopping centers, restaurants, parks and recreational facilities.
